structural regular expressions:

    - the Edit command from the last slide looked a lot like a normal sed expression:

          Edit , s/mouse/clicky thing/g

    - but the syntax supported in ad is a lot richer than you might expect

    - the command language here is inspired by the one found in another plan 9 text editor, sam

        http://sam.cat-v.org/

        Edit 18,28 y/\n\n/ x/@*occupation: programmer@*/ x/name: (.*)/ p/$1 is a programmer/


name: Alice
occupation: programmer
language of choice: Rust

name: Bob
occupation: programmer
language of choice: Go

name: Claire
occupation: linguist
language of choice: French
